    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hand-sized cups having a bowl shape, usually without a handle, used for drinking tea; sometimes accompanied by a matching saucer. Often, but not always, from Asia or having an Asian theme.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
